- Remote Sensing: Companies related to earth observation, satellite imaging, and geospatial technology; 
- Machine Learning: Companies that focus on data-driven AI solutions, such as computer vision and natural language processing; 
- Water Resource: Companies related to water resource management, such as water conservation, analysis, and purification. 
You can also pursue projects related to water resource management, such as developing an AI-driven system to monitor water resources or developing algorithms to analyze water quality data. You can also work at organizations that use remote sensing and machine learning to solve water-related problems. 
In addition, you could also work at companies that use machine learning to develop models for predicting water resource dynamics.
